Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! What should I do? This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just whine, help me pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can someone please help me pick these up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, they're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this tiny idiot's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong, Aisaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga really loves Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks she has to be good because Santa is always watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All girls love Christmas, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two finding time to study for your exams with all these party preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we've been studying as a group recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Aisaka-san always has good grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your grades are always good too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Haruta-kun, Haruta-kun and Haruta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Haruta-kun too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun hasn't been helping with the preparations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura ordered him to stay out of this so he could study.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you two won't let your grades drop, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried that you two might be spending too much time on the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, are you coming to the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any dates on Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the sake of my pride, I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really hope it's a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are putting a lot of effort into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll definitely reap the rewards!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.59,0:02:06.77,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)\pos(894.545455,492)}Beneath the Fir Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Taiga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minorin! Club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We spent the whole time working out in the gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, hurry up or the coach will start complaining again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we really haven't been talking much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party will definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin is being really weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll definitely cheer up if she comes to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do our best to make it an amazing party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's do it, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So slow! What were you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got held up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of the ornaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Go redo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, should you really be saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you trying to be good for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The P.E. teacher asked us to clean out the storeroom in return for letting us use the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let me care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura, make the stars with Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, scissors and glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold scissors like that, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, they sure are getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go and help out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.39,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what are they trying to stir up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Stir what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb, you know I'm talking about Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... liking Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately it seems like everyone is trying to pair them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really obsessed with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why would I be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get pissed off when outsiders spread stuff about someone else's love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how a father feels when his daughter is about to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know. It's not like I have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I've never met my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not allowing her to fall, get hurt, or cry."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Watching the most precious woman of your life get taken away from you by another man."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not knowing if that man will treasure her as much as you do."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely it won't be fun for you to watch Yuusaku and Taiga date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the total opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not her father, but you treasure the woman you're determined not to lay a hand on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already have another woman in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like playing house. You three know exactly which characters you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like pretending to be daddy, mommy and the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to pretend to be daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship with Taiga seems really unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should stop playing this childish game of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been making mistakes all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wake up before you get hurt even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should forget everything and just start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could also give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend you didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget everything I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, what you really don't understand is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.76,Chalk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(596,138,645,138)\frz15}English Final
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, put your pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's over! It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.69,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.19,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta, you're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down and listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.69,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas! Christmas is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's normal school tomorrow and the day after,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't get too excited about Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to have lunch with Ryuuji and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have to go to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, Minorin has club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for turning you guys down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just seems like we haven't had a chance to talk lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, Taiga and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our Coach was taken over by the dark side, so now our practice is harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to create a chance for you guys to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we had left and arrived at the shop, I'd be like "Sorry, I have something to do!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even planned a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Taiga sure is passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There {\i1}will{\i0} be another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat something before we go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't going to lie, I really have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I go home to get something, I need to go to the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you don't need{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to have a talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come and have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Sorry, I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to the post office with her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ryuuji! I said you didn't need to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what's with that gal girl pretending to be Kitamura's childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant, the honest girl, Kihara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, it won't be a lie if I go to the post office with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The thing you need to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you plan to take them all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are none of your concern; just help me get the cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.32,Hand,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(746,240)\frz340\c&H4D5158&}To: Aisaka Rikurou (Father)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.65,Hand,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,198)\frz17\c&H535A61&}To: Aisaka Yuu (Stepmother)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't Christmas, I would've beaten you up already,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the sake of being good, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Christmas presents for {\i1}that{\i0} family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're planning to give them another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because of that, it's because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they're my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also got presents for you and Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you want to say, but I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.16,Hand,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,198)\frz17\c&H535A61&}From: Santa Claus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.60,Plain,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,204)\frz7}5th in line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to an all-girls Catholic school all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was rejected by the high school because of bad behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that school, you have to do volunteer work with the sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to put it this way, but we play with orphans and do some other odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The present with "Santa" written on it is actually for those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, presents for {\i1}that{\i0} family, and now for orphans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I don't understand you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell them that there are people who are watching over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas is a chance to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if you don't have parents and don't believe in God...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, there's someone watching over you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want to show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to know that someone cares about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You're right. It's self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's because I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone is actually watching over me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, that person is Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa, Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly love Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The streets, shops... Everywhere is glittering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dazzling and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone looks really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is overflowing with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm part of that happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be part of the happy, glittering scene on Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while wearing a happy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really met Santa before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was on a Christmas Eve when my parents were still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sleeping under the Christmas tree in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up because it was cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I looked out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me a present and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Be a good child and I'll definitely come again."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it might have been a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, it was a really happy dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm stupid for believing in a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, it's not like it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm clinging to something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The Christmas tree is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be amazing once we put it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the party will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-chan, are you going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not going for the sake of my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I should buy a present for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watches, bags, or even accessories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a reward for thirty years of hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking that I'm wasting money, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking that I'm just a single woman who's falling for advertising tactics, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't waste money because I need seventy million yen for retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if I stop myself from buying things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm finally all "Yay! I have a hundred million yen!",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but before I know it, inflation in Japan gets so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that all the money I've saved becomes useless{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?! I just predicted the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I should buy myself an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check if we have all the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you managed to get something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a decoration in a model show I was on, so I asked them if I could have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're a stupid chi-, but you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best tree ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one could disagree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even better once we put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come on, let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the supporting parts all right like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the top part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san, you look pretty light,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so can you get on my back and put this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the shoes I just went to the toilet with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Different people really do have different interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dozing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure, I think this is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that for?! It was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your reflexes are pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the Palmtop Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}But it's because I believe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}someone is actually watching over me somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you didn't actually have someone watching over you for the past seventeen years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also have Yasuko, Inko-chan, and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, Kushieda will definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}You'll definitely reap the rewards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we'll get rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone will get rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this from my house; put it on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful... Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it looks really expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is my favorite decoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't put it on my own Christmas tree because it was too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it on carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackout curtains are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power source is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, turn off the lights now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one got hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident, it couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, you're not at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an unfortunate accident{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was because I spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost control of the ball and it broke something very important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I might not be able to fix it, just let me do whatever I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let Ryuuji hel{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you help me, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not helping you, I'm just doing what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun... Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be fixed even if it's broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't put it back to how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it can be fixed no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cuter than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come to the party tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go after all the trouble I caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait for you!
