Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy night! Holy night! Holy night! Holy night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! It's a party on the holy night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want more fruit punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Taiga?
